nodes.text: Knights of the Old Republic (Star Wars Miniatures)

The Knights of the Old Republic set of Star Wars Miniatures contains 60 miniatures from the Old Republic era. The set was expected to be released August 7, 2008 but was pushed to August 19. The booster cover art was done by Terese Nielsen. The full set list was published on the Wizards of the Coast website one month prior to its release.
Rarity denoted as follows: Common (C), Uncommon (U), Rare (R), Very Rare (VR)
